Singer/song writer Kingsley Okonkwo aka KCee was a year older on April 18. KCee who has always kept his family away from attention, had a photo session with his wife and two children and shared the beautiful photos online to celebrate his birthday. He wrote on the photos: “I found the greatest fortune on earth by having you all as my back bone, thank you all for being everything I wanted in a family. Thank you all for being steadfast all the times I was absent giving to the nature of my job, thank you all for always loving me excessively even in the midst of my imperfections. This is showbizflair’s pick from the photos shared